Definition of Automated Code Generation System
----------------------------------------------------------------------

For the purposes of this license, an "Automated Code Generation System"
means any software, platform, or service that automatically generates
source code, applications, APIs, services, or other software artifacts
from spreadsheets, models, schemas, specifications, or other structured
non-code inputs.

Examples include but are not limited to:

- Spreadsheet-to-code generators
- Model-to-code platforms
- Configuration-to-code systems
- Services that automatically generate software for users

